Project1.Title: System Proposal
Project1.Desc:
I wrote this system proposal document for my "CSC3150 - Systems Design" class.

It proposes an application I wish to build to optimize meals and walk chefs through recipes. Its primary goal is to help chefs take notes while walking them through recipes and to help them notice beneficial patterns when recipe results vary. The proposal includes a broad overview of the application and its features.

Project2.Title: System Specification document
Project2.Desc:
I wrote this system specification document for my "CSC3150 - Systems Design" class.

It specifies the details of an application designed to optimize meals and walk chefs through recipes. The document contains a much more detailed view of this application and includes detailed user interface documents.
